1. Oni *služe* u crkvi nedeljom. (They serve in the church on Sundays.)
2. Konzerve *služe* kao dobra hrana u kampovanju. (Canned food serves as good food while camping.)
3. U restoranu *služe* ukusnu hranu. (They serve delicious food in the restaurant.)
4. Radnici *služe* klijentima u banci. (Employees serve clients in the bank.)
5. Vojska *služi* svojoj zemlji. (The military serves their country.)
6. Hvala ti što *služiš* ovom jelu. (Thank you for serving this dish.)
7. Oni *su služili* u vojsci zajedno. (They served in the military together.)
8. Imam nekoliko tanjira koji *služe* za posebne prilike. (I have several plates that serve for special occasions.)
9. U restoranu, konobari *služe* goste. (In the restaurant, waiters serve guests.)
10. Naš telefon *služi* i kao budilnik. (Our phone serves as an alarm clock too.)